				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">What do bards want?<a name="25723"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 5 04 12:45 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi, all.  I'm very new to the game of EQ and have been working to get information from all classes.  I have rolled a shaman and would like to know - straight from the bard's flute (so to speak) - when grouping with a shaman, what do you generally expect?  What spells do you need most from a shaman?  Do you prefer to slow before the shaman slows?  Any advice you can give me would be much appreciated.
<br />
<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> 
<br />
Adelai</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
